dct_description_sm: This tabular data represent rates of homeownership by Hispanic and Latino Individuals in the city of Milwaukee, Wisconsin for 2022. This data set is part of a collection of Milwaukee Indicators hosted by Data You Can You, in collaboration with the Community Development Alliance.
